data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: U.S. Marines with Marine Aircraft Group (MAG) 12 participate in the Harpoon training exercise aboard Marine Corps Air Station Iwakuni, Apr. 28, 2020. MAG-12 focused on naval missions and simulated anti-ship long range fires in order to enhance the Marine Corps’ ability to effect sea control and denial in the Indo-Pacific. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Lance Cpl. Jackson Ricker and Pfc. Katie Markwald)
